<Unit>
<Name> Working on a Living Application
<Comment> mark insert 1.0 mark current 1.0 text {One very } 1.0 mark anchor 1.9 text {useful feature of Tcl is its ability to substitute procedures. When a procedure is reloaded, the new definition replaces the old definition in the application code. You can therefore change the running application with a click on the Load button.
} 1.9 text {
} 2.0 text {This can be a great help when you are testing variations of a function. You don't need to restart the application again and again, and each time reestablish the state of the program that you are testing. When you Load the changed source, the state is preserved; you are ready to test the change immediately. 
} 3.0 text {
